name: Vintage/Nautical Style Swimsuit White/Navy 1503
description:
Don't like to "show-off" too much, but still want to be sexy!? This casual swimsuit features a fuller cut in the leg and rear area for maximum comfort. The contrast waistband and side panel gives just enough flair without being over stated!

"Sleek" Style Low-Rise Square Cut Swimsuit. Fully lined front and back. Built in comfort pouch at center seam. Measurement at Side Seams 7", Inseam width 4". Drawstring. 3/4" Elastic Waistband.

80% Nylon 20% Spandex Hand Wash Cold, Lay Flat To Dry. Do Not Dry Clean or Tumble Dry. 

PLEASE SPECIFY YOUR SIZE WHEN PURCHASING YOUR SWIMSUIT!

XSMALL 26-27
SMALL 28-30
MEDIUM 31-32
LARGE 33-34
X-LARGE 36

ALL WAIST SIZES ARE IN INCHES. PLEASE NOTE THESE SWIMSUITS SHOULD FIT SNUGGLY AGAINST YOUR BODY.

name: Vintage Box Cut Swimsuit Green Stripe 1403
description:
Box-Cut Swimsuit. True Vintage cut, just like in the 40's and 50's.

Flattering on every man! Scrunch it down for wearing lower on your waist. Fully lined Front, Back and Gusset (between the legs). Pocket on right leg, just the right size for your phone and room key!

.75" elastic rolled waistband. Drawstring. Fully lined (front & back) with drawstring.

80% Nylon 20% Spandex 
Lining 100% Nylon
Hand Wash Cold, Lay Flat To Dry. Do Not Dry Clean or Tumble Dry.
